[30;1m56 | [0m[35m    The "format_version" field stands for the format of the JSON file. For now[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m    it is always "1". The `private_key_id` and `private_key` is used for signing.[0m
[30;1m58 | [0m[35m    The `ca_cert_path` is used for token server TLS certificate verification.[0m
[30;1m59 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m60 | [0m[35m    After the JSON file is created, set `GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS` environment[0m

[30;1m149 | [0m[35m    """On-demand JWT credentials.[0m
[30;1m150 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m151 | [0m[35m    Like :class:`Credentials`, this class uses a JWT as the bearer token for[0m
[30;1m152 | [0m[35m    authentication. However, this class does not require the audience at[0m
[30;1m153 | [0m[35m    construction time. Instead, it will generate a new token on-demand for[0m
[30;1m154 | [0m[35m    each request using the request URI as the audience. It caches tokens[0m
[30;1m155 | [0m[35m    so that multiple requests to the same URI do not incur the overhead[0m
[30;1m156 | [0m[35m    of generating a new token every time.[0m
